				</div>
			</div>
			<p uri="/ensign/2007/05/the-spirit-of-the-tabernacle.p79" class="">I add my testimony that Jesus is the Christ, that this is His house, on this sacred day of dedication in the name of Jesus Christ, amen.</p>
		
                            
                            
                            
